snippet.textDisplay: Coke Studio started as an experiment to bring different singers together. In India, it adds more rhythm because of various genres of music - classical, hindustani, folk music, regional etc. Madari is a superb combination of some folk, hindustani & western music. Clinton has combined Vishal's husky rock-style voice well with Sonu Kakkar's high-pitched classical vocals to bring this amazing track. The composition and arrangements are simply superb. Great work by the Coke Studio team. Thumbs up !
snippet.textOriginal: Coke Studio started as an experiment to bring different singers together. In India, it adds more rhythm because of various genres of music - classical, hindustani, folk music, regional etc. Madari is a superb combination of some folk, hindustani & western music.
